						<p>On a pillar of the <hi rend="italic">maṇḍapa</hi> in front of the central shrine in the Śingāravallabhasvāmin temple.</p>						

						<p>This is dated Śaka 1327, Āshāḍha, śu. 2, Sunday.</p>						

						<p>Records the gift of a pillar to the temple of Śriṅgārarāya by a certain Lakkasāni, daughter of Kāḷakēśu.</p>						

